You can’t weight the existing index P/E and stock P/E... you need to harmonic weight them (i.e. 1 / PE x weight of each, then flip back). 

If S&P 500 is 23x and $TSLA is 500x it’s 1 / (98.2% x 1/23) + (1.8% x 1/500) = 23.4x
